{"tid":481770,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人道vs法律","createTime":"2017-11-27T13:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T01:11:41.000Z","uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5adeac80630486126a4ac8992e7d8ff69d8dda4d","tid":481770,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"假如打仗嗰陣,你身邊個隊友畀人炸開咗個肚,佢明知自己救唔返,哀求你開槍打死佢, 如果你接受會唔會有機會畀人告謀殺?<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dddcc5df38a79c7e38738579e246c5e4f75f6c4","tid":481770,"uid":146541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"都打仗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236fc9cf12922e4df0e207a0e61b763a74d494c1","tid":481770,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c408427fc07eb7e3a77b242e13981859ba586b1e","tid":481770,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>士可殺 不可辱 同埋戰爭有戰爭法 應該唔係用平時嗰套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係想問會唔會奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7408f1a2668f3ba4997a6fa22fa191663c697a","tid":481770,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"負皮嘅唔該畀解釋"},{"pid":"e5a929e60e940fc49b7de8f4868269df275750bc","tid":481770,"uid":150611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0cdf024a37a0ec591d581d97622be019003a256","tid":481770,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"死因係比敵人炸死，仲要友方士兵頂罪<br />\n咁嘅法律執柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"67352176a8a645ccc1778f452d164fd94afa72c7","tid":481770,"uid":156544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:01:44.000Z","msg":"為左幫朋友 捨身取義"},{"pid":"5703c7a41e50193a657554cc6dffb91fdca517ac","tid":481770,"uid":32826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:22:36.000Z","msg":"打緊仗跟乜撚野法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8854caa68748a00b34affd6bf3a2b9e944a963be","tid":481770,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打緊仗跟乜撚野法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁MP死㗎?<br />\n即使二戰德國都有遵守國際法, 雖然係選擇性執行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b527968182cc18c95e147f09f6f5ac0de153368","tid":481770,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:36:22.000Z","msg":"世界上係有軍事法庭呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13131cb83bd802f49c617bcf02a747c4f5679626","tid":481770,"uid":47463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T23:24:38.000Z","msg":"其實國際嘅法庭嘅裁決(例如紐倫堡法庭、海牙、Strasbourg嘅裁決)同埋international conventions (例如ECHR之類)<br />\n對於唔少國家<br />\n都只係有political influence 但唔係legally binding<br />\n又或者該國家嘅legislature有冇立法給予依啲相關嘅international law/convention喺國內有實際嘅法律權力同行使同意權<br />\n如果冇嘅話 一切以政治（國家利益、形象）為首<br />\n英國就係一個好例子<br />\n<br />\n但係唔講international野嘅話<br />\n好多國家都有喺本土homocide嘅法律上有講戰時嘅處理會有唔同<br />\n因國家而異"},{"pid":"2deb2d68e097b1914953a3c1cc6cf42dc3c763ac","tid":481770,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T23:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實國際嘅法庭嘅裁決(例如紐倫堡法庭、海牙、Strasbourg嘅裁決)同埋international conventions (例如ECHR之類)<br />\n對於唔少國家<br />\n都只係有political influence 但唔係legally binding<br />\n又或者該國家嘅legislature有冇立法給予依啲相關嘅international law/convention喺國內有實際嘅法律權力同行使同意權<br />\n如果冇嘅話 一切以政治（國家利益、形象）為首<br />\n英國就係一個好例子<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">所以即使軍事法庭、人權法庭之類裁定該次戰爭中嘅killing係unlawful<br />\n都唔代表嗰條友一定會受罰</span><br />\n<br />\n但係唔講international野嘅話<br />\n好多國家都有喺本土homocide嘅法律上有講戰時嘅處理會有唔同<br />\n因國家而異<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">有啲國家仲會寫明殺敵軍唔係罪行</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">利申 唔係識好多 有錯請指</span>"},{"pid":"235d318f2e3b1c98b78f1ffbe7a13767a0675b6a","tid":481770,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實國際嘅法庭嘅裁決(例如紐倫堡法庭、海牙、Strasbourg嘅裁決)同埋international conventions (例如ECHR之類)<br />\n對於唔少國家<br />\n都只係有political influence 但唔係legally binding<br />\n又或者該國家嘅legislature有冇立法給予依啲相關嘅international law/convention喺國內有實際嘅法律權力同行使同意權<br />\n如果冇嘅話 一切以政治（國家利益、形象）為首<br />\n英國就係一個好例子<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">所以即使軍事法庭、人權法庭之類裁定該次戰爭中嘅killing係unlawful<br />\n都唔代表嗰條友一定會受罰</span><br />\n<br />\n但係唔講international野嘅話<br />\n好多國家都有喺本土homocide嘅法律上有講戰時嘅處理會有唔同<br />\n因國家而異<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">有啲國家仲會寫明殺敵軍唔係罪行</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">利申 唔係識好多 有錯請指</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}